Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:30.67,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&H60&}那漸次熄滅的星光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:34.38,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&H60&}或許從最初開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:36.47,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&H60&}終結的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:41.39,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&H60&}就已從夢境深處凝視著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:46.52,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&H60&}懷揣著已然空洞的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:50.69,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&H60&}不斷思索著悲傷的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.69,0:00:54.20,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&H60&}體內迸發的煙火光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:58.16,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&H60&}正灼傷著我們的視線
